Package: MRStdLCRT
Type: Package
Title: Model-Robust Standardization for Stepped-wedge Cluster-Randomized Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xi", "Fang", email = "x.fang@yale.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Estimation and leave-one-cluster-out jackknife standard errors for
    four crossover estimands—horizontal individual ATE (h-iATE), horizontal cluster ATE (h-cATE),
    vertical individual ATE (v-iATE), and vertical cluster-period ATE (v-cATE)—via
    unadjusted and augmented (model-robust standardization) approaches.
    Supports continuous outcomes via linear mixed models and binary outcomes via GEE or GLMM.
    Optionally excludes the first and last periods when aggregating estimands (stepped-wedge style).
